          <fr:mainmatter><fr:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f\colon  A\to  B]]></fr:tex> be a <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-000Y.xml" title="Section-retraction pair" addr="//erct/erct-000Y" type="local">retraction</fr:link> of some <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s\colon  B\to  A]]></fr:tex>; the type of <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-000Y.xml" title="Section-retraction pair" addr="//erct/erct-000Y" type="local">retractions</fr:link> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex> is, then, a <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001I.xml" title="Proposition" addr="//erct/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link>.</fr:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree show-metadata="false" toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link href="foreign-erct-jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="//erct/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:date><fr:year>2023</fr:year><fr:month>12</fr:month><fr:day>31</fr:day></fr:date><fr:anchor>9023</fr:anchor><fr:addr type="machine">//erct/unstable/466</fr:addr><fr:route>foreign-erct-unstable-466.xml</fr:route><fr:title text="" /><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
 <fr:p>Analogous to the <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-002Q.xml" title="Sections of sections are unique" addr="//erct/erct-002Q" type="local">corresponding result for sections of sections</fr:link>, using the fact that the type of <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-000Y.xml" title="Section-retraction pair" addr="//erct/erct-000Y" type="local">retractions</fr:link> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex> can be seen to be a <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-0025.xml" title="Retract" addr="//erct/erct-0025" type="local">retract</fr:link> of the <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001Q.xml" title="Fiber" addr="//erct/erct-001Q" type="local">fiber</fr:link> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[-\circ  f]]></fr:tex> at <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[1_{A}]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
